  <brief_title>Minimally Invasive Open Preperitoneal Surgery With Polysoft Mesh Versus a Classic Open Surgery With Light Weight Mesh</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Study to Evaluate the Recovery of a Hernia Inguinalis by a Minimally Invasive Open Preperitoneal Surgery With Polysoft Mesh Versus a Classic Open Surgery According to Modified Lichtenstein Procedure With Light Weight Mesh</official_title>
