  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective randomized study to evaluate the recovery of a hernia inguinalis by a
      minimally invasive open preperitoneal surgery with polysoft mesh versus a classic open
      surgery according to modified Lichtenstein procedure with light weight mesh.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
